{"id":"605859","title":"时停五百年","writer":"作梦DR","dateline":"1563605736","updatetime":"1563605736","isover":"1","filesize":"2962599","linecount":"20418","wordcount":"978592","imgpath":"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/UTB8ZFVDxT_IXKJkSalUq6yBzVXak.jpg","hash":"shiting5bainian","urlhash":"txtnvl_3852988","sign":"","desc":"《时停五百年》作者：作梦DR \n起点VIP2018-12-18完结\n简介：\n 神打算把地球做成一个游戏，而为了避免人类在游戏制作过程中死掉，神把全球人类的时间都暂停了，但唯独魏获的时间没有被停。\n五百年后，游戏《人类崛起》开服，魔族玩家降临，传奇人类出现，而魏获，已经在这个游戏里领先了他们五百年。\n      标签：游戏异界 二次元 学生 魔兽\n[domain]","hot":"0","num":"0","cid":"92","suggcate":"网游,竞技,游戏,游戏异界","suggcids":"92,101,98,98","notbook":"0","fetchv":"0","lasthot":"0","clicknum":"0","isvip":"1","ish":"0","age":"现代","channel":"男","isqiniu":"0","list":"0,2o3,5ki,8eh,am3,df6,ggr,izq,ls5,nns,py5,scv,ufs,wm9,zb6,11pg,148w,17ct,1a12,1cm9,1eru,1hu4,1kpd,1mna,1otw,1r2r,1tn5,1w5g,1y3r,20iq,239a,25ht,27wo,2abo,2c7f,2eh6,2h6b,2jur,2mpw,2p3e,2rug,2u6x,2wov,2zar,31t7,34cs,36m0,395d,3blp,3eb2,3h54,3js1,3lyk,3o0e,3qk0,3sy6,3uxa,3xd8,4010,42l2,45qe,481f,4aqs,4d9a,4fw2,4i9t,4khz,4mqg,4phz,4s0h,4urg,4x1e,4zix,51zl,54s2,577n,59ur,5c27,5e91,5gk8,5ivi,5l9d,5ng7,5pv1,5sfl,5uvz,5xdw,5zdu,6184,630h,64qz,6710,69f3,6bzb,6e3g,6fxe,6i7s,6ksp,6mvt,6pig,6ril,6tmv,6w9v,6yc5,70s9,73mx,75zy,7894,7afo,7cmj,7ewl,7hlu,7k6a,7mog,7pba,7s6z,7uks,7xdg,7zme,81sq,84ef,8754,89x6,8d0e,8ftl,8i7l,8kw1,8nr0,8qwq,8u2f,8wxl,8zto,92i9,956b,97zl,9auq,9ddy,9fx8,9is0,9kw5,9n2s,9piz,9rkh,9tfl,9w76,9yg7,a142,a45x,a6u8,a9zj,acn1,afl1,aj07,alh2,antf,aq4f,at3y,avlr,axvt,b0pl,b3qf,b6dz,b8mf,bari,bd8z,bfjc,bids,bla9,bo6w,bql3,bth6,bvul,bynu,c1nj,c4l0,c6se,c99p,cbsc,ce9i,cgqa,cjh0,cm84,codv,cqxs,ctta,cxcd,d04g,d3a8,d6bo,d97d,dbgp,ddp7,dgm3,djff,dm0b,don9,dra4,dttt,dwuh,dzp4,e2ix,e569,e7k9,eage,ed4b,eg2g,eiqv,em06,eobp,equq,etmh,ewbr,eyxn,f1fk,f3y5,f6mf,f8wk,fbpe,femz,fh8y,fju5,fmuw,fphj,fs14,fuqv,fxml,g0p1,g3e1,g6cp,g9fz,gc1q,geyx,ghn6,gk8t,gmh7,gp40,grpq,gujf,gx98,h03c,h3cg,h6f1,h9m9,hcxa,hfyj,hjaq,hm4f,hpei,hsfr,hvt5,hysq,i1k5,i4jl,i7x6,iap1,ie6m,ihun,ikfp,ineh,iqxv,itn